**【快乐聊】Android端下载安装通用教程**

1，打开QQ浏览器，若没有QQ浏览器在手机的APP市场里下载安装

2，打开QQ浏览器

![image](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331153309180.png)

![image-20200331153309180](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331153309180.png)

3，清空浏览器缓存，选择“文件”，点击"安装包"

![image-20200331153640823](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331153640823.png)

4,点击右下角"一键清理“安装包，进行清空所有

![image-20200331153741039](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331153741039.png)

5，选择”首页“，点击”输入框“

![image-20200331154110235](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331154110235.png)

6，粘贴下载地址：https://kxlbucket.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/temp/app_kxlv39_release.apk 并点击”进入“按钮
![image-20200331154257249](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331154257249.png)

7，弹窗下载提示框，点击”直接下载“按钮

![image-20200331154345982](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331154345982.png)

8，下载完成会自动跳转安装提示，点击”设置“

![image-20200331154620655](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331154620655.png)

9，打开”允许安装应用“开关（蓝色代表打开状态），并点击左上角返回箭头

![image-20200331154720028](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331154720028.png)

10，点击”安装“按钮，安装快乐聊APP

![image-20200331154913193](http://git.3nn1.com/xiaohua/happyim/raw/master/pic/image-20200331154913193.png)
